Name: C64 & AMIGA Classix Remakes Sixpack 3
About the game: Get some of the classic games from the 80s and 90s back on your home PC - as a remake. Enjoy again the unforgettable fun of the past time! - Remakes of your favourite classics of the C64 and AMIGA era - Contains the 6 retro classics: - Star Taxi Remake - Eypx Peng Remake - Turrican Lode Jumper Remake - Bomberwarrior Remake - Mos Garden Remake - Moon Battle Remake
